snippet.textDisplay: I watched your video from last year a few weeks ago and I wish I had known about your project to do it again this year! I just moved to New York City and I've had six packages stolen in the five months that I've lived here. I try my hardest to have them rerouted or picked up but sometimes I don't know that I'm receiving a package until it's too late :/  I even had a package stolen from my front door while I was at home (within minutes!!!). I am so upset at this point I have tried to create little inventions like this on my own but I am nowhere near as tech-savvy as you are so I've just given up on ordering things unless I know they're going to be delivered by UPS...in which case I can have them rerouted to my local pharmacy. Losing all the packages especially when I'm a broke college student doesn't feel great but this video sure makes up for it!
